rComments: Professor was OK for the course. He is too serious to be professor, but he knows the course content, particularly when it comes to international aspects. Easy mark if you study the slides. No textbook which is hard for students.

Very boring, I don't think I was ever able to listen for more than 2 minutes. Everything you need is in the slides so saying that attending class is useless is an understatement. His course notes were disorganized and riddled with mistakes, sometimes to the point where they were incomprehensible. Silver-lining, easy A if you study the slides.
